This is a detoxification pill
made by Yumei.

15
00:01:58,550 --> 00:01:59,390
That's great.

16
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:00,630
Commander is saved.

17
00:02:03,270 --> 00:02:05,190
This pill's effect
is not that significant.

18
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,160
It's just some calming medicine

19
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,910
to make him feel better
during the withdrawal.

20
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:15,240
The rest is up to him to endure.

21
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,200
Xingzhou.

22
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:29,830
Xingzhou, you will get better.

23
00:02:29,830 --> 00:02:30,960
I can't take it anymore.

24
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,030
- Xingzhou.
- Opium.

25
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:33,880
Let me have a smoke. Just one.

26
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,080
Xingzhou, you will get better.

27
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:38,320
I can't get better.

28
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,520
I can't get better.

29
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,110
